<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type'/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>
			Congratulations <%= @participant.name %>
		</h1>
		<p>
			You have been chosen as a winner for the giveaway <%= @giveaway.title %> that you have joined previously.
		</p>
		<%if @giveaway.winner_message.present? %>
			<p><%=  @giveaway.winner_message %></p>
		<% end %>
		<p>
			Expect an email soon from <%= @giveaway.company.name %> for further instructions for prize collection.
		</p>
		<p>
			Meanwhile please visit
			<% if @giveaway.company.website.present? %>
				<%= @giveaway.company.website %> if you would like to learn more about them.
			<% else %>
				<%= @giveaway.company.social_media_link[0] %> f you would like to learn more the affiliated company.
			<% end %>
		</p>
		<br>
		<p>
			Congratulations,<br>
			The Gift2Grow Team.
		</p>
		<p><span style="font-size: 10px;">
			Disclaimer: Gift2Grow is not responsible for the exchange process between the selected winner and responsible company.
		</span></p>
	</body>
</html>